-- Citigroup Must Be Ready for Any Outcome on Euro, Telegraph Says
-- B y   M a r i a   K o l e s n i k o v a
-- 2012-07-15T07:14:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-15/citigroup-must-be-ready-for-any-outcome-on-euro-telegraph-says.html
Citigroup Inc. “must be ready for
any eventuality” on the euro and the region’s debt crisis,
Chief Executive Officer  Vikram Pandit  told the Sunday Telegraph
in an interview.  “Our perspective continues to be one where we would like
to see a unified Europe, a strong fiscal unified Europe,”
Pandit said, according to the Telegraph.  To contact the reporter on this story:
